channel.title: [REQ] -Dodain- How do I change where a teleport teleports me!? -Dodain- [REQ]
channel.description:
Howdy. I found out on my own how to change the starting/death coords. NOW, I need to change the teleport coords! :|
Tell me how, and I'll Rep you. ;) :D

item.title: [REQ] -Dodain- How do I change where a teleport teleports me!? -Dodain- [REQ]
item.dc:creator: @Explisionist Explisionist
item.description:
@Explisionist wrote:

Who cares about rep… and first you open client.java … and search the tele that u wana change such as yanille, dragon cave, legends guide, etc… then change that name to what you want… and then search for that tele again… if its not there then search gahorak or how ever u spell it… and then you will see cords for them… the first one is the very first tele on the ancients list, and so on…
